item.title: CVE-2021-26605|2024-08-03T20:26:25.550Z -- unidocs -- ezpdfreader
item.description: An improper input validation vulnerability in the service of ezPDFReader allows attacker to execute arbitrary command. This issue occurred when the ezPDF launcher received and executed crafted input values through JSON-RPC communication.
